data.description: Looking for a peaceful & private retreat, this is the home just for you! Fabulous waterfront 4 bed 3 full bath cabin nested on 14 acres with stocked spring fed pond with bass, catfish & brim! Spectacular views from the huge front porch making everyday living feel like paradise plus walkway to the home features a koi pond! Beautiful hardwood flooring! Living room with vaulted ceiling & stove fireplace! Kitchen with granite countertops, breakfast bar, walk in pantry, range, built in microwave, dishwasher, chef's sink & refrigerator stays! Large dining room with nice ceiling fan & custom dining table that is negotiable! Owners suite with ceiling fan, walk in closet & nearby full bathroom with with double sink vanity & jetted tub! Two additional spare bedrooms on main level! Second full bathroom! Upstairs 4th bedroom with full bathroom with closet, would also make a great game room! Sconces throughout & updated ceiling fans! Laundry enclosed under the stairwell with central vac system! Side entry two car garage that is heated/cooled! Sprinkler system in the fenced area! Lumber for the home came from the land! Property has muscadine, blueberry, apple & pear! Under deck has area for cleaning fish! High speed internet available! This home is an absolute must see!
